All the Watchers regroup on the bridge.

Watcher 1: I think she was telling the truth, I didn&#39;t see anyone else.

Watcher 2: We better get them back to base quickly. They need a CR chamber.

Watcher 3: We could reprogram them also. This femmebot has already given us access to her spark, whether she knows it or not.

The fourth Watcher is quiet while he studies Rodimus Prime.

Watcher 4: We must be quick about this. It would be best if no other factions learned that these two were here yet.

Watcher 1: What is so important about these two?

Watcher 4: I am suprised that you did not pick up on your history yet.

Watcher 1: What do you mean?

Watcher 4 points at Rodimus Prime.

Watcher 4: This one is an Autobot. Not just any Autobot, either. He is Hot Rod, the chosen one of the ancient Matrix prophecy. This one became Rodimus Prime and used the Matrix to destroy Unicron. He was one of the first Targetmasters. At last report he had been leading the Maximal faction here on Pre-Earth during the Neo Beast Wars. He had disspeared by the time Transformers started colonizing here.

Watcher 1: So we got us a sure fire legend on our hands, eh? Get them to base and repaired now.

Lord Elder(via commlink): When they have awakened from repairs send them to me.

Watcher 1: You heard him. Lets get this done.

The Watchers procede as ordered.


